Definition: a witty satiric verse containing two rhymed couplets and mentioning a famous person
Example: `The president is George W. Bush, Who is happy to sit on his tush, While sending his armies to fight, For anything he thinks is right' is a clerihew
Synonyms: verse, a, witty, satiric, containing, two, rhymed, couplets, and, mentioning, famous, person, The, president, is, George, W, Bush, Who, happy, to, sit, on, his, tush, While, sending, armies, fight, For, anything, he, thinks, right
Category: noun.communication
